mockMessages.content: Hello! I'm Dr. Johnson and I need help with a patient case.
Hello Dr. Johnson! I'd be happy to help you with your patient case. Please provide me with the relevant details and I'll do my best to assist you with medical insights and guidance.
Can you help me debug this React component?
Absolutely! I'd be happy to help you debug your React component. Please share the code and describe the issue you're experiencing, and I'll help you identify and fix the problem.
I need to calculate the load capacity for this bridge design.

I can help you with structural engineering calculations for your bridge design. Please provide me with the specifications, materials, dimensions, and loading conditions, and I'll assist you with the load capacity analysis.
